				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					<p>I know you can edit a text file in a &lt;textarea&gt; with the following code I got from:</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href='http://www.dynamicdrive.com/forums/showthread.php?4539-how-do-i-modify-existing-txt-files-with-php' class='bbc_url' title='External link' rel='external'>http://www.dynamicdr...-files-with-php</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p></p><pre  class="prettyprint linenums:0">&nbsp;
&lt;?&nbsp;
&nbsp;if($_POST&#91;'Submit']){&nbsp;
&nbsp; $open = fopen("textfile.txt","w+");&nbsp;
&nbsp; $text = $_POST&#91;'update'];&nbsp;
&nbsp; fwrite($open, $text);&nbsp;
&nbsp; fclose($open);&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "File updated.&lt;br /&gt;"; &nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "File:&lt;br /&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; $file = file("textfile.txt");&nbsp;
&nbsp; foreach($file as $text) {&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;echo $text."&lt;br /&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; }&nbsp;
&nbsp;}
&nbsp;else{&nbsp;
&nbsp; $file = file("textfile.txt");&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "&lt;form action=\"".$PHP_SELF."\" method=\"post\"&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "&lt;textarea Name=\"update\" cols=\"50\" rows=\"10\"&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; foreach($file as $text) {&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;echo $text;&nbsp;
&nbsp; } &nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "&lt;/textarea&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "&lt;input name=\"Submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Update\" /&gt;\n&nbsp;
&nbsp; &lt;/form&gt;"; &nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;}&nbsp;
?&gt;
</pre>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>I'm thinking is it possible to&nbsp;edit a <u><em>specific record</em></u> in a text file in a &lt;textarea&gt;.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p></p><pre  class="prettyprint linenums:0">&nbsp;

&lt;?&nbsp;
&nbsp;//### Process edit_textform
&nbsp;error_reporting(-1);
&nbsp;//### Define Variable
&nbsp;$filename = "repair_upgrade.txt";
&nbsp;$path = $_SERVER&#91;'DOCUMENT_ROOT']."/home/users/web/b686/dom.horacela/public_html/";
&nbsp;$searchfor = preg_replace('#&#91;\D]#', '', $confirmation_number);
&nbsp;//### Get Data From Form
&nbsp;$confirmation_number = isset($_POST&#91;'confirmation_number']) ? $_POST&#91;'confirmation_number'] : FALSE ;
&nbsp;//### Validate confirmation number
&nbsp;if(empty($confirmation_number)) {
&nbsp; echo 'No confirmation number.'. PHP_EOL;
&nbsp; exit;
&nbsp;}&nbsp;
&nbsp;else {
&nbsp; //### Remove anything that is a not a number
&nbsp; $confirmation_number = preg_replace('#&#91;\D]#', '', $confirmation_number);
&nbsp;}
&nbsp;//### Check if file is writable
&nbsp;if(!is_writable($filename)) {
&nbsp; echo 'The file is not writable.'. PHP_EOL;
&nbsp; exit;
&nbsp;}
&nbsp;//### Check if file is readable
&nbsp;if (!is_readable($filename)) {
&nbsp; echo 'The file is not readable'. PHP_EOL;
&nbsp; exit;
&nbsp;} &nbsp;
&nbsp;elseif($searchfor) != FALSE) {
&nbsp; //### Search file for Confirmation_number.&nbsp;
&nbsp; $file = file($filename); &nbsp;
&nbsp; //### Set pointer to current record
&nbsp; fseek($file, SEEK_CUR);
&nbsp; echo "&lt;form action=\"".$PHP_SELF."\" method=\"post\"&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo "&lt;textarea Name=\"update\" cols=\"50\" rows=\"10\"&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; While(!preg_match('/\bEND\b/i',$file)) {
&nbsp; &nbsp;foreach($file as $text) {&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp; echo $text;&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;}
&nbsp; } &nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp; echo " &lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n";
&nbsp; echo " &lt;input name=\"Submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Update\" /&gt;\n &lt;/form&gt;\n";&nbsp;
&nbsp;}
&nbsp;else {
&nbsp; if($_POST&#91;'Submit']){&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;$open = fopen($filename,"a+");&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;$text = $_POST&#91;'update'];&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;fwrite($open, $text);&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;fclose($open);&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;echo "File updated.&lt;br /&gt;"; &nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;echo "File: $filename &lt;br /&gt;";
&nbsp; } 
&nbsp; $file = file($filename);&nbsp;
&nbsp; foreach($file as $text) {&nbsp;
&nbsp; &nbsp;echo $text."&lt;br /&gt;";&nbsp;
&nbsp; }
&nbsp; fclose($fh);
&nbsp;}
?&gt;

</pre>
